fields.title: Inception (2010)
fields.description: A skilled thief is offered a chance to have his criminal history erased if he can plant an idea into a target's subconscious.

fields.title: Interstellar (2014)
fields.description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

fields.title: The Dark Knight (2008)
fields.description: When the menace known as the Joker emerges, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

fields.title: Inside Out 2
fields.description: Riley's mind headquarters welcomes new emotions as she navigates teenage life, friendships, and personal growth.

fields.title: Deadpool & Wolverine
fields.description: Deadpool teams up with Wolverine in a chaotic multiverse adventure, blending humor, action, and fan-favorite characters.

fields.title: Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning
fields.description: Hunt and the IMF pursue a dangerous AI called the Entity that's infiltrated global intelligence. With governments and a figure from his past in pursuit, Hunt races to stop it from forever changing the world.

fields.title: The Batman: Part II
fields.description: Bruce Wayne returns to Gotham’s shadows to confront new threats in this darker, noir-inspired sequel to The Batman (2022).

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Sorcerer’s Stone
fields.description: Harry Potter, an orphaned boy living with his unkind relatives, discovers on his 11th birthday that he is a wizard. He attends Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry, where he uncovers the truth about his parents’ mysterious deaths and confronts dark forces for the first time.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets
fields.description: Harry returns to Hogwarts despite warnings of danger. When students are mysteriously petrified, he and his friends must uncover the secrets of the Chamber and face a deadly threat from the school’s past.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban
fields.description: Harry learns that Sirius Black, a dangerous prisoner, has escaped from Azkaban and may be after him. As secrets about his family unfold, he learns the truth about friendship, loyalty, and betrayal.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
fields.description: When Harry is unexpectedly entered into the dangerous Triwizard Tournament, he must compete against older and more experienced students while a dark force begins to rise again.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix
fields.description: As the Ministry of Magic denies the return of Voldemort, Harry and his friends form 'Dumbledore’s Army' to prepare for the looming battle.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince
fields.description: As Voldemort tightens his grip on both the wizarding and Muggle worlds, Harry uncovers a crucial secret that may be key to defeating him, while Dumbledore prepares for the final battle.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 1
fields.description: Harry, Ron, and Hermione leave Hogwarts behind to hunt down Voldemort’s Horcruxes, but their friendship is tested as danger and despair close in.

fields.title: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2
fields.description: The epic conclusion to the Harry Potter saga. Harry and his friends make their final stand against Voldemort in the Battle of Hogwarts. Sacrifices are made, truths are revealed, and destinies fulfilled.

fields.title: My Daughter Is a Zombie
fields.description: Lee Jeong Hwan, a fierce animal trainer, lives a chaotic daily life with his rebellious teenage daughter, Lee Su A, who is full of passion for dancing. One day, Su A becomes infected by a zombie virus that has swept across the globe.

fields.title: Project Y
fields.description: Two women are friends and of the same age. They make an audacious plan to steal $6 million USD in gold bars and flee from the area.

fields.title: No Other Choice
fields.description: After being unemployed for several years, a man devises a unique plan to secure a new job: eliminate his competition.

fields.title: Zootopia
fields.description: In a city of anthropomorphic animals, a rookie bunny cop and a cynical con artist fox must work together to uncover a conspiracy.
